import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-landing', standalone: true, imports: [CommonModule], templateUrl: './landing.component.html' }) export class LandingComponent { constructor(private router: Router) {} goToRegister() { this.router.navigate(['/register']); } goToLogin() { this.router.navigate(['/login']); } }

üè¢ Process Management System

Manage your company's business processes efficiently

Welcome!

This system helps you document, manage, and visualize your company's business processes.

üìã How It Works

1

Register Your Company

Create an account for your organization. An admin user will be created automatically.

2

Create Roles

Define roles like "Analyst", "Supervisor", "Manager" that will be responsible for activities.

3

Document Processes

Create processes and add activities, decision points (gateways), and connections (arcs).

4

Invite Team Members

Add users to your company with different permission levels (Admin, Editor, Read-only).

‚ú® Features

üîê Multi-Company

Each company has its own isolated data

üë• User Management

Invite users and assign roles

üìä Process Modeling

Create activities, gateways, and arcs

üéØ Role Assignment

Assign responsibilities to roles

üìù Draft & Publish

Work on drafts before publishing

üîç Search & Filter

Find processes by category

üöÄ Quick Start Guide

Step 1: Click "Register Your Company" and fill in your company details
Step 2: Login with your admin credentials
Step 3: Go to "Manage Roles" and create at least one role (e.g., "Analyst")
Step 4: Go to "Manage Processes" and create your first process
Step 5: Click "Details" on your process to add activities and gateways

Ready to get started?
